{
  "video_id": "j3YjeARuilI",
  "title": "Enrique Pe√±alosa: Why buses represent democracy in action",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12245.0,
      "end_time": 15378.0,
      "text": "Mobility in developing world cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15378.0,
      "end_time": 17536.0,
      "text": "is a very peculiar challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17536.0,
      "end_time": 19341.0,
      "text": "because different from health"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19341.0,
      "end_time": 21651.0,
      "text": "or education or housing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21651.0,
      "end_time": 25850.0,
      "text": "it tends to get worse as societies become richer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25850.0,
      "end_time": 27869.0,
      "text": "Clearly, a unsustainable model."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27869.0,
      "end_time": 32195.0,
      "text": "Mobility, as most other developing country problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32195.0,
      "end_time": 36101.0,
      "text": "more than a matter of money or technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36101.0,
      "end_time": 41492.0,
      "text": "is a matter of equality, equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41492.0,
      "end_time": 44601.0,
      "text": "The great inequality in developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44601.0,
      "end_time": 48250.0,
      "text": "makes it difficult to see, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50590.0,
      "text": "that in terms of transport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50590.0,
      "end_time": 52520.0,
      "text": "an advanced city is not one"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52520.0,
      "end_time": 54542.0,
      "text": "where even the poor use cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54542.0,
      "end_time": 56565.0,
      "text": "but rather one where even the rich"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56565.0,
      "end_time": 58789.0,
      "text": "use public transport."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58789.0,
      "end_time": 62355.0,
      "text": "Or bicycles: For example, in Amsterdam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62355.0,
      "end_time": 64384.0,
      "text": "more than 30 percent of the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64385.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65920.0,
      "text": "uses bicycles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65920.0,
      "end_time": 67818.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that the Netherlands has"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67818.0,
      "end_time": 71801.0,
      "text": "a higher income per capita than the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71801.0,
      "end_time": 75658.0,
      "text": "There is a conflict in developing world cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75658.0,
      "end_time": 78226.0,
      "text": "for money, for government investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78226.0,
      "end_time": 80727.0,
      "text": "If more money is invested in highways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80727.0,
      "end_time": 82739.0,
      "text": "of course there is less money for housing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82739.0,
      "end_time": 85960.0,
      "text": "for schools, for hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 89720.0,
      "text": "and also there is a conflict for space."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89720.0,
      "end_time": 91498.0,
      "text": "There is a conflict for space between"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91498.0,
      "end_time": 94230.0,
      "text": "those with cars and those without them."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94230.0,
      "end_time": 95866.0,
      "text": "Most of us accept today"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95866.0,
      "end_time": 98650.0,
      "text": "that private property and a market economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98650.0,
      "end_time": 101848.0,
      "text": "is the best way to manage most of society&#39;s resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101848.0,
      "end_time": 104253.0,
      "text": "However, there is a problem with that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104253.0,
      "end_time": 106921.0,
      "text": "that market economy needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106921.0,
      "end_time": 109639.0,
      "text": "inequality of income in order to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109639.0,
      "end_time": 111181.0,
      "text": "Some people must make more money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111181.0,
      "end_time": 112732.0,
      "text": "some others less."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112732.0,
      "end_time": 115301.0,
      "text": "Some companies succeed. Others fail."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115301.0,
      "end_time": 117175.0,
      "text": "Then what kind of equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117175.0,
      "end_time": 118780.0,
      "text": "can we hope for today"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118780.0,
      "end_time": 120702.0,
      "text": "with a market economy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120702.0,
      "end_time": 122638.0,
      "text": "I would propose two kinds"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122638.0,
      "end_time": 124992.0,
      "text": "which both have much to do with cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124992.0,
      "end_time": 128980.0,
      "text": "The first one is equality of quality of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128979.99999999999,
      "end_time": 129885.99999999999,
      "text": "especially for children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129886.0,
      "end_time": 131541.0,
      "text": "that all children should have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131541.0,
      "end_time": 134548.0,
      "text": "beyond the obvious health and education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134548.0,
      "end_time": 138407.0,
      "text": "access to green spaces, to sports facilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138407.0,
      "end_time": 141433.0,
      "text": "to swimming pools, to music lessons."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 141433.0,
      "end_time": 143924.0,
      "text": "And the second kind of equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143924.0,
      "end_time": 148207.0,
      "text": "is one which we could call \"democratic equality.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148207.0,
      "end_time": 151156.0,
      "text": "The first article in every constitution states"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151156.0,
      "end_time": 154445.0,
      "text": "that all citizens are equal before the law."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154445.0,
      "end_time": 156900.0,
      "text": "That is not just poetry."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156900.0,
      "end_time": 159101.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very powerful principle."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159101.0,
      "end_time": 161687.0,
      "text": "For example, if that is true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161687.0,
      "end_time": 163572.0,
      "text": "a bus with 80 passengers"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163572.0,
      "end_time": 166301.0,
      "text": "has a right to 80 times more road space"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 166301.0,
      "end_time": 169173.0,
      "text": "than a car with one."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 169173.0,
      "end_time": 173566.0,
      "text": "We have been so used to inequality, sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 173566.0,
      "end_time": 177297.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s before our noses and we do not see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 177297.0,
      "end_time": 179573.0,
      "text": "Less than 100 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 179573.0,
      "end_time": 180960.0,
      "text": "women could not vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180960.0,
      "end_time": 183166.0,
      "text": "and it seemed normal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 183166.0,
      "end_time": 186850.0,
      "text": "in the same way that it seems normal today"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186850.0,
      "end_time": 189781.0,
      "text": "to see a bus in traffic."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189782.0,
      "end_time": 192733.0,
      "text": "In fact, when I became mayor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192733.0,
      "end_time": 195701.0,
      "text": "applying that democratic principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 195701.0,
      "end_time": 198113.0,
      "text": "that public good prevails over private interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198113.0,
      "end_time": 201130.0,
      "text": "that a bus with 100 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 201130.0,
      "end_time": 203587.0,
      "text": "has a right to 100 times more road space than a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 203587.0,
      "end_time": 206601.0,
      "text": "we implemented a mass transit system"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 206601.0,
      "end_time": 209700.0,
      "text": "based on buses in exclusive lanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209700.0,
      "end_time": 213512.0,
      "text": "We called it TransMilenio, in order to make buses sexier."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213512.0,
      "end_time": 221309.0,
      "text": "And one thing is that it is also a very beautiful democratic symbol, because as buses zoom by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221309.0,
      "end_time": 225472.0,
      "text": "expensive cars stuck in traffic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225473.0,
      "end_time": 231800.0,
      "text": "it clearly is almost a picture of democracy at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231800.0,
      "end_time": 235629.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s not just a matter of equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235629.0,
      "end_time": 237521.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t take Ph.D.&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 237521.0,
      "end_time": 239792.0,
      "text": "A committee of 12-year-old children"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 239793.0,
      "end_time": 241799.0,
      "text": "would find out in 20 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241799.0,
      "end_time": 245503.0,
      "text": "that the most efficient way to use scarce road space"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245503.0,
      "end_time": 248987.0,
      "text": "is with exclusive lanes for buses."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248987.0,
      "end_time": 252309.0,
      "text": "In fact, buses are not sexy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 252309.0,
      "end_time": 255456.0,
      "text": "but they are the only possible means"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 255456.0,
      "end_time": 258738.0,
      "text": "to bring mass transit to all areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 258738.0,
      "end_time": 262414.0,
      "text": "of fast growing developing cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262414.0,
      "end_time": 264589.0,
      "text": "They also have great capacity."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 264589.0,
      "end_time": 267333.0,
      "text": "For example, this system in Guangzhou"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267333.0,
      "end_time": 270380.0,
      "text": "is moving more passengers our direction"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270380.0,
      "end_time": 272862.0,
      "text": "than all subway lines in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 272862.0,
      "end_time": 275353.0,
      "text": "except for one line in Beijing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275353.0,
      "end_time": 277690.0,
      "text": "at a fraction of the cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 277690.0,
      "end_time": 281804.0,
      "text": "We fought not just for space for buses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 281804.0,
      "end_time": 284859.0,
      "text": "but we fought for space for people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284860.0,
      "end_time": 288730.0,
      "text": "and that was even more difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288730.0,
      "end_time": 290858.0,
      "text": "Cities are human habitats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290858.0,
      "end_time": 294587.0,
      "text": "and we humans are pedestrians."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294587.0,
      "end_time": 297651.0,
      "text": "Just as fish need to swim or birds need to fly"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297651.0,
      "end_time": 300443.0,
      "text": "or deer need to run, we need to walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 300443.0,
      "end_time": 303774.0,
      "text": "There is a really enormous conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 303774.0,
      "end_time": 306775.0,
      "text": "when we are talking about developing country cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306775.0,
      "end_time": 309453.0,
      "text": "between pedestrians and cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309454.0,
      "end_time": 312385.0,
      "text": "Here, what you see is a picture that shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 312385.0,
      "end_time": 314370.0,
      "text": "insufficient democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 314370.0,
      "end_time": 317128.0,
      "text": "What this shows is that people who walk"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 317129.0,
      "end_time": 318804.0,
      "text": "are third-class citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 318804.0,
      "end_time": 320138.0,
      "text": "while those who go in cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 320139.0,
      "end_time": 321954.0,
      "text": "are first-class citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 321954.0,
      "end_time": 324361.0,
      "text": "In terms of transport infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 324361.0,
      "end_time": 325563.0,
      "text": "what really makes a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 325564.0,
      "end_time": 328110.0,
      "text": "between advanced and backward cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 328110.0,
      "end_time": 330202.0,
      "text": "is not highways or subways"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 330202.0,
      "end_time": 332466.0,
      "text": "but quality sidewalks."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 332466.0,
      "end_time": 335232.0,
      "text": "Here they made a flyover, probably very useless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 335232.0,
      "end_time": 339190.0,
      "text": "and they forgot to make a sidewalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 339190.0,
      "end_time": 341514.0,
      "text": "This is prevailing all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 341514.0,
      "end_time": 345299.0,
      "text": "Not even schoolchildren are more important than cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 345299.0,
      "end_time": 347539.0,
      "text": "In my city of Bogot√°,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 347540.0,
      "end_time": 350894.0,
      "text": "we fought a very difficult battle"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 350894.0,
      "end_time": 353668.0,
      "text": "in order to take space from cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 353668.0,
      "end_time": 356564.0,
      "text": "which had been parking on sidewalks for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 356564.0,
      "end_time": 359679.0,
      "text": "in order to make space for people that should reflect"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 359679.0,
      "end_time": 361347.0,
      "text": "dignity of human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 361347.0,
      "end_time": 364195.0,
      "text": "and to make space for protected bikeways."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 364196.0,
      "end_time": 366941.0,
      "text": "First of all, I had black hair before that."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 366941.0,
      "end_time": 368917.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 368917.0,
      "end_time": 372172.0,
      "text": "And I was almost impeached in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 372173.0,
      "end_time": 374317.0,
      "text": "It is a very difficult battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 374317.0,
      "end_time": 377494.0,
      "text": "However, it was possible, finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 377494.0,
      "end_time": 380732.0,
      "text": "after very difficult battles, to make a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 380732.0,
      "end_time": 383416.0,
      "text": "that would reflect some respect for human dignity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 383416.0,
      "end_time": 385211.0,
      "text": "that would show that those who walk are equally"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 385211.0,
      "end_time": 387320.0,
      "text": "important to those who have cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 387320.0,
      "end_time": 391681.0,
      "text": "Indeed, a very important ideological and political issue anywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 391681.0,
      "end_time": 394627.0,
      "text": "is how to distribute that most valuable resource"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 394627.0,
      "end_time": 397360.0,
      "text": "of a city, which is road space."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 397360.0,
      "end_time": 399873.0,
      "text": "A city could find oil or diamonds underground"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 399873.0,
      "end_time": 401964.0,
      "text": "and it would not be so valuable as road space."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 401964.0,
      "end_time": 405125.0,
      "text": "How to distribute it between pedestrians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 405125.0,
      "end_time": 408227.0,
      "text": "bicycles, public transport and cars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 408227.0,
      "end_time": 411180.0,
      "text": "This is not a technological issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 411180.0,
      "end_time": 414542.0,
      "text": "and we should remember that in no constitution"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 414542.0,
      "end_time": 416863.0,
      "text": "parking is a constitutional right"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 416863.0,
      "end_time": 419364.0,
      "text": "when we make that distribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 419364.0,
      "end_time": 422994.0,
      "text": "We also built, and this was 15 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 422995.0,
      "end_time": 424933.0,
      "text": "before there were bikeways in New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 424933.0,
      "end_time": 426377.0,
      "text": "or in Paris or in London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 426377.0,
      "end_time": 428824.0,
      "text": "it was a very difficult battle as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 428824.0,
      "end_time": 433644.0,
      "text": "more than 350 kilometers of protected bicycle ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 433644.0,
      "end_time": 435568.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think protected bicycle ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 435568.0,
      "end_time": 438322.0,
      "text": "are a cute architectural feature."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 438322.0,
      "end_time": 441280.0,
      "text": "They are a right, just as sidewalks are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 441280.0,
      "end_time": 443226.0,
      "text": "unless we believe that only those"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 443226.0,
      "end_time": 445560.0,
      "text": "with access to a motor vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 445560.0,
      "end_time": 447627.0,
      "text": "have a right to safe mobility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 447627.0,
      "end_time": 449900.0,
      "text": "without the risk of getting killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 449900.0,
      "end_time": 453566.0,
      "text": "And just as busways are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 453567.0,
      "end_time": 455658.0,
      "text": "protected bikeways also are"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 455658.0,
      "end_time": 457537.0,
      "text": "a powerful symbol of democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 457537.0,
      "end_time": 461186.0,
      "text": "because they show that a citizen on a $30 bicycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 461187.0,
      "end_time": 463609.0,
      "text": "is equally important"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 463609.0,
      "end_time": 467551.0,
      "text": "to one in a $30,000 car."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 467551.0,
      "end_time": 471268.0,
      "text": "And we are living in a unique moment in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 471268.0,
      "end_time": 475719.0,
      "text": "In the next 50 years, more than half of those cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 475720.0,
      "end_time": 480282.0,
      "text": "which will exist in the year 2060 will be built."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 480282.0,
      "end_time": 482580.0,
      "text": "In many developing country cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 482580.0,
      "end_time": 484640.0,
      "text": "more than 80 and 90 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 484640.0,
      "end_time": 489342.0,
      "text": "of the city which will exist in 2060"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 489342.0,
      "end_time": 491703.0,
      "text": "will be built over the next four or five decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 491703.0,
      "end_time": 494825.0,
      "text": "But this is not just a matter for developing country cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 494825.0,
      "end_time": 496813.0,
      "text": "In the United States, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 496814.0,
      "end_time": 499479.0,
      "text": "more than 70 million new homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 499479.0,
      "end_time": 502176.0,
      "text": "must be built over the next 40 or 50 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 502176.0,
      "end_time": 505248.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s more than all the homes that today exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 505249.0,
      "end_time": 509765.0,
      "text": "in Britain, France and Canada put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 509765.0,
      "end_time": 513121.0,
      "text": "And I believe that our cities today"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 513121.0,
      "end_time": 515236.0,
      "text": "have severe flaws,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 515236.0,
      "end_time": 518794.0,
      "text": "and that different, better ones could be built."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 518794.0,
      "end_time": 521242.0,
      "text": "What is wrong with our cities today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 521243.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525477.0,
      "text": "Well, for example, if we tell any three-year-old child"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 525477.0,
      "end_time": 527182.0,
      "text": "who is barely learning to speak"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 527182.0,
      "end_time": 528693.0,
      "text": "in any city in the world today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 528693.0,
      "end_time": 530375.0,
      "text": "\"Watch out, a car,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 530375.0,
      "end_time": 532937.0,
      "text": "the child will jump in fright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 532937.0,
      "end_time": 534716.0,
      "text": "and with a very good reason, because there are"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 534716.0,
      "end_time": 537273.0,
      "text": "more than 10,000 children who are killed"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 537273.0,
      "end_time": 540742.0,
      "text": "by cars every year in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 540742.0,
      "end_time": 543349.0,
      "text": "We have had cities for 8,000 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 543350.0,
      "end_time": 547686.0,
      "text": "and children could walk out of home and play."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 547686.0,
      "end_time": 549978.0,
      "text": "In fact, only very recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 549978.0,
      "end_time": 551811.0,
      "text": "towards 1900, there were no cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 551812.0,
      "end_time": 555813.0,
      "text": "Cars have been here for really less than 100 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 555813.0,
      "end_time": 558587.0,
      "text": "They completely changed cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 558587.0,
      "end_time": 560535.0,
      "text": "In 1900, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 560535.0,
      "end_time": 564420.0,
      "text": "nobody was killed by cars in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 564421.0,
      "end_time": 566336.0,
      "text": "Only 20 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 566336.0,
      "end_time": 569731.0,
      "text": "between 1920 and 1930,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 569731.0,
      "end_time": 572890.0,
      "text": "almost 200,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 572890.0,
      "end_time": 574599.0,
      "text": "were killed by cars in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 574599.0,
      "end_time": 578630.0,
      "text": "Only in 1925, almost 7,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 578630.0,
      "end_time": 582582.0,
      "text": "were killed by cars in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 582582.0,
      "end_time": 586585.0,
      "text": "So we could make different cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 586585.0,
      "end_time": 589346.0,
      "text": "cities that will give more priority to human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 589346.0,
      "end_time": 591805.0,
      "text": "than to cars, that will give more public space"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 591805.0,
      "end_time": 593929.0,
      "text": "to human beings than to cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 593929.0,
      "end_time": 596684.0,
      "text": "cities which show great respect"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 596684.0,
      "end_time": 598844.0,
      "text": "for those most vulnerable citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 598845.0,
      "end_time": 600629.0,
      "text": "such as children or the elderly."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 600629.0,
      "end_time": 604434.0,
      "text": "I will propose to you a couple of ingredients"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 604434.0,
      "end_time": 607776.0,
      "text": "which I think would make cities much better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 607776.0,
      "end_time": 610261.0,
      "text": "and it would be very simple to implement them"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 610261.0,
      "end_time": 613185.0,
      "text": "in the new cities which are only being created."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 613185.0,
      "end_time": 616238.0,
      "text": "Hundreds of kilometers of greenways"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 616238.0,
      "end_time": 619388.0,
      "text": "criss-crossing cities in all directions."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 619388.0,
      "end_time": 622132.0,
      "text": "Children will walk out of homes into safe spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 622132.0,
      "end_time": 625930.0,
      "text": "They could go for dozens of kilometers safely"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 625930.0,
      "end_time": 628146.0,
      "text": "without any risk in wonderful greenways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 628147.0,
      "end_time": 630563.0,
      "text": "sort of bicycle highways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 630563.0,
      "end_time": 633668.0,
      "text": "and I would invite you to imagine the following:"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 633668.0,
      "end_time": 636906.0,
      "text": "a city in which every other street would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 636906.0,
      "end_time": 641977.0,
      "text": "a street only for pedestrians and bicycles."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 641992.0,
      "end_time": 644223.0,
      "text": "In new cities which are going to be built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 644223.0,
      "end_time": 646767.0,
      "text": "this would not be particularly difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 646768.0,
      "end_time": 650295.0,
      "text": "When I was mayor of Bogot√°,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 650295.0,
      "end_time": 652824.0,
      "text": "in only three years, we were able to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 652825.0,
      "end_time": 654963.0,
      "text": "70 kilometers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 654963.0,
      "end_time": 657459.0,
      "text": "in one of the most dense cities in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 657459.0,
      "end_time": 659825.0,
      "text": "of these bicycle highways."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 659826.0,
      "end_time": 663216.0,
      "text": "And this changes the way people live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 663216.0,
      "end_time": 665888.0,
      "text": "move, enjoy the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 665888.0,
      "end_time": 668509.0,
      "text": "In this picture, you see in one of the very poor neighborhoods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 668509.0,
      "end_time": 671579.0,
      "text": "we have a luxury pedestrian bicycle street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 671579.0,
      "end_time": 673939.0,
      "text": "and the cars still in the mud."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 673940.0,
      "end_time": 676763.0,
      "text": "Of course, I would love to pave this street for cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 676763.0,
      "end_time": 678211.0,
      "text": "But what do we do first?"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 678211.0,
      "end_time": 681372.0,
      "text": "Ninety-nine percent of the people in those neighborhoods don&#39;t have cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 681372.0,
      "end_time": 683844.0,
      "text": "But you see, when a city is only being created,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 683845.0,
      "end_time": 685935.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very easy to incorporate"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 685935.0,
      "end_time": 688111.0,
      "text": "this kind of infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 688111.0,
      "end_time": 690809.0,
      "text": "Then the city grows around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 690809.0,
      "end_time": 693852.0,
      "text": "And of course this is just a glimpse"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 693852.0,
      "end_time": 696646.0,
      "text": "of something which could be much better"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 696647.0,
      "end_time": 698365.0,
      "text": "if we just create it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 698365.0,
      "end_time": 700702.0,
      "text": "and it changes the way of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 700702.0,
      "end_time": 704768.0,
      "text": "And the second ingredient, which would solve mobility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 704768.0,
      "end_time": 707346.0,
      "text": "that very difficult challenge in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 707346.0,
      "end_time": 710341.0,
      "text": "in a very low-cost and simple way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 710341.0,
      "end_time": 714353.0,
      "text": "would be to have hundreds of kilometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 714353.0,
      "end_time": 716875.0,
      "text": "of streets only for buses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 716875.0,
      "end_time": 719979.0,
      "text": "buses and bicycles and pedestrians."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 719979.0,
      "end_time": 723180.0,
      "text": "This would be, again, a very low-cost solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 723180.0,
      "end_time": 725341.0,
      "text": "if implemented from the start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 725341.0,
      "end_time": 727864.0,
      "text": "low cost, pleasant transit"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 727864.0,
      "end_time": 731562.0,
      "text": "with natural sunlight."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 731562.0,
      "end_time": 736210.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, reality is not as good"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 736210.0,
      "end_time": 737962.0,
      "text": "as my dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 737962.0,
      "end_time": 741144.0,
      "text": "Because of private property of land"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 741144.0,
      "end_time": 744165.0,
      "text": "and high land prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 744165.0,
      "end_time": 747202.0,
      "text": "all developing country cities have a large problem of slums."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 747202.0,
      "end_time": 750112.0,
      "text": "In my country of Colombia, almost half the homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 750112.0,
      "end_time": 755458.0,
      "text": "in cities initially were illegal developments."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 755458.0,
      "end_time": 758670.0,
      "text": "And of course it&#39;s very difficult to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 758670.0,
      "end_time": 762626.0,
      "text": "mass transit or to use bicycles in such environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 762626.0,
      "end_time": 764672.0,
      "text": "But even legal developments"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 764672.0,
      "end_time": 767644.0,
      "text": "have also been located in the wrong places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 767644.0,
      "end_time": 770445.0,
      "text": "very far from the city centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 770445.0,
      "end_time": 772482.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s impossible to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 772482.0,
      "end_time": 776313.0,
      "text": "low-cost, high-frequency public transport."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 776313.0,
      "end_time": 779193.0,
      "text": "As a Latin American, and Latin America"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 779193.0,
      "end_time": 782620.0,
      "text": "was the most recently organized region in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 782620.0,
      "end_time": 787780.0,
      "text": "I would recommend, respectfully, passionately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 787780.0,
      "end_time": 791890.0,
      "text": "to those countries which are yet to urbanize --"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 791890.0,
      "end_time": 796911.0,
      "text": "Latin America went from 40 percent urban in 1950"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 796911.0,
      "end_time": 802983.0,
      "text": "to 80 percent urban in 2010 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 802984.0,
      "end_time": 806144.0,
      "text": "I would recommend Asian and African countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 806144.0,
      "end_time": 807926.0,
      "text": "which are yet to urbanize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 807926.0,
      "end_time": 812930.0,
      "text": "such as India which is only 33 percent urban now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 812930.0,
      "end_time": 815680.0,
      "text": "that governments should acquire all land around cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 815680.0,
      "end_time": 817589.0,
      "text": "In this way, their cities could grow in the right places"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 817589.0,
      "end_time": 819364.0,
      "text": "with the right spaces, with the parks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 819364.0,
      "end_time": 822740.0,
      "text": "with the greenways, with the busways."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 822740.0,
      "end_time": 824255.0,
      "text": "The cities we are going to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 824255.0,
      "end_time": 826950.0,
      "text": "over the next 50 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 826950.0,
      "end_time": 828492.0,
      "text": "will determine quality of life and even happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 828492.0,
      "end_time": 830646.0,
      "text": "for billions of people towards the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 830646.0,
      "end_time": 834223.0,
      "text": "What a fantastic opportunity for leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 834224.0,
      "end_time": 836466.0,
      "text": "and many young leaders to come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 836466.0,
      "end_time": 838533.0,
      "text": "especially in the developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 838533.0,
      "end_time": 840380.0,
      "text": "They can create a much happier life"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 840380.0,
      "end_time": 841949.0,
      "text": "for billions towards the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 841949.0,
      "end_time": 843911.0,
      "text": "I am sure, I am optimistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 843912.0,
      "end_time": 845820.0,
      "text": "that they will make cities better"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 845820.0,
      "end_time": 848989.0,
      "text": "than our most ambitious dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 848989.0,
      "end_time": 852866.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}